---
title: Creamy Chicken & Spinach Pasta with Garlic Pangrattato & Turnip Salad
description: This saucy creation uses a flavourful creamy sauce to coat fusilli, with chunks of tender chicken and garlic-herb seasoning. Add
baby spinach that gently wilts when tossed with the pasta, and you’ve got a new recipe that's sure to please everyone.
